[13.481706, "o", "╭────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────╮\r\n│                                                                                        │\r\n│                            YES  —  Medium confidence (74%)                             │\r\n│                                                                                        │\r\n╰────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────╯\r\n"]
[13.484162, "o", "  Leaning YES. 3/5 agents agree (medium confidence), but there are counterarguments worth \r\nconsidering.\r\n\r\n"]
[13.484573, "o", "────────────────────────────────────────── Why ───────────────────────────────────────────\r\n"]
[13.484835, "o", "  1. B2B creates defensible revenue.\r\n"]
[13.485101, "o", "  2. B2B ACV of $24k vs B2C LTV of $180.\r\n"]
[13.485395, "o", "  3. Hybrid approach: keep B2C running on autopilot, dedicate 5 of 8 engineers to B2B \r\npilot.\r\n"]
[13.48545, "o", "\r\n"]
[13.486209, "o", "──────────────────────────────────────── Top Risk ────────────────────────────────────────\r\n"]
[13.486783, "o", "  No enterprise sales infrastructure exists. Pivoting without SOC 2, SLAs, or a sales team\r\nis a recipe for burning remaining runway."]
[13.486842, "o", "\r\n\r\n"]
[13.487271, "o", "  ████████████████████████████████████████  3 for / 1 against / 1 undecided\r\n"]
[13.487325, "o", "\r\n"]
[13.487611, "o", "  MAJORITY · 4.1s · swarm-agency v1.0.0\r\n"]
[13.487657, "o", "\r\n"]
[13.48812, "o", "\r\n──── Full Agent Deliberation ────\r\n"]
[13.489533, "o", "\r\n\r\n────────────────────────────────────── SWARM AGENCY ──────────────────────────────────────\r\n\r\n╭─────────────────────────────────────── QUESTION ───────────────────────────────────────╮\r\n│                                                                                        │\r\n│   Should we pivot from B2C to B2B?                                                     │\r\n│                                                                                        │\r\n╰────────────────────────── 5 agents · 5 models · Demo · 4.1s ───────────────────────────╯\r\n"]
[13.493541, "o", "  Context: B2C growth flat at 12k MAU for 6 months. Enterprise inbound up 3x. Team of 8. \r\n14 months runway.\r\n\r\n╭────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────╮\r\n│                                 📊  MAJORITY: APPROVE                                  │\r\n╰────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────╯\r\n  Confidence: █████████████████████████████░░░░░░░░░░░ 74%\r\n\r\n  Summary: Strategy department recommends pivot with conditions. 3 approve (Visionary, \r\nGrowthHacker, Pragmatist), 1 rejects (DevilsAdvocate citing execution risk), 1 neutral \r\n(NumbersCruncher wanting data). Recommended: 90-day hybrid pilot before full commitment.\r\n"]
